author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! I can't believe the extent some of the biggest companies in the world will go to to ensure we see nothing but the most annoying advertisements anywhere we go. This time I'm not shocked but rather appalled to see that Samsung is now sticking them in devices that cost well into the premium. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: They're Putting Ads In Our Fridges Now...
